<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .content { margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Teachease Africa!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for applying to our {{courseName}} program. We're excited to have you join us!</p>
      <p>Your application has been received and is being processed. Here are your application details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Course: {{courseName}}</li>
        <li>Schedule: {{courseSchedule}}</li>
        <li>Duration: {{courseDuration}}</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will contact you shortly with further instructions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>Teachease Africa Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>